          <div class="faq">
            <div class="grid-container">
              <div class="grid-x grid-padding-x">
                <div class="large-10 cell">
                  <h4>What is format agency and how does it work?</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="large-2 cell">
                  <img class="arrow show-for-large" src="img/arrow.png">
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid-container info">
              <div class="grid-x grid-padding-x">
                <div class="large-12 cell">
                  <p>Think of Format like “Content-as-a-Service” for your business.  We provide professional services for any number of business sectors, from health and medicine to financial technology.</p>
        <p>As paid acquisition channels become more and more saturated (and therefore increasingly costly and unreliable), organic traffic is becoming more important to companies looking to grow sustainably.  Our content programs and SEO expertise will help your company be the top resource in your niche.</p>
        <p>For a flat-fee, we provide a full SEO audit for you and your business — and for a monthly fee, we accelerate your SEO vital signals for search engines to near perfect SEO indicators within 90 days. We will provide expert driven content articles, refactor your blog, and go through our proprietary 33-point checklist to ensure that you are set up for long-term customer acquisition and success with SEO. A set-it-and-(almost)-forget-it content strategy.*</p>
        <p>We see ourselves as a longterm partner for our clients in this area, and tailor our service to each specific business model and goal.</p>
        <p>*We say set-it-and-(almost)-forget-it because we advise that each team have an internal resource to spend ~30 minutes/per article proofreading and publishing live to your customers and potential customers.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq">
            <div class="grid-container">
              <div class="grid-x grid-padding-x">
                <div class="large-10 cell">
                  <h4>What are the services and price points provided by format agency?</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="large-2 cell">
                  <img class="arrow show-for-large" src="img/arrow.png">
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid-container info">
              <div class="grid-x grid-padding-x">
                <div class="large-12 cell">
                  <p>Format Agency will provide our proprietary <a href="files/SEO-Checklist.pdf" target="_blank">33-point checklist</a> audit to give you a sense for how your content (from homepage to product pages to blog posts) will perform with various search engines.</p>
        <p>After the initial SEO audit, Format’s content creation operates in a two tiered approach:</p>
        <ol>
        <li>First three months: optimized site and blog delivered with 30 articles published and live
          <ol type="a">
          <li>Site optimization</li>
          <li>Blog setup</li>
          <li>Strategic build-out of 50-150 search terms (depending on industry/sector)</li>
          <li>30 articles live based on the strategic search terms</li>
          <li>Backlink recommendations</li>
          <li>Proprietary checklist for optimization</li>
          <li>Centralized key metric visualization</li>
          <li>Bi-weekly check ins with updates and strategic suggestions</li>
          </ol>
        </li>
        <li>Following the initial three month period, we will continue to buiild on the initial successes we have seen and scale to reach performance marks that we lay out during our initial conversations.    
        </li>
        <li>Pricing upon request.</li>
        </ol>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq">
            <div class="grid-container">
              <div class="grid-x grid-padding-x ">
                <div class="large-10 cell">
                  <h4>What does the process look like?</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="large-2 cell">
                  <img class="arrow show-for-large" src="img/arrow.png">
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid-container info">
              <div class="grid-x grid-padding-x">
                <div class="large-12 cell">
        <p>Audit:</p>
        <p>The initial audit phase will take approximately 5-10 days.  We will schedule an initial call to chat about your brand, what your customers and competitive set looks like, what particular keywords you would like to rank for, etc...  We will then run through our SEO checklist to determine the status of your current SEO effort.</p>   

        <p>Format Program:</p>
        <p>Once you have committed to our Content-as-a-Service program, we will determine which topics to write about based on keyword groupings and areas of opportunity we uncovered in the audit.  From there we will generate content that will allow you to not only rank for these keywords, but be the source of truth in your niche for your current and potential customers.  You can expect 30 high-quality articles published and live at the end of 90-days, and clear signal on where we can proceed with the SEO effort.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq">
            <div class="grid-container">
              <div class="grid-x grid-padding-x">
                <div class="large-10 cell">
                  <h4>How will I know how this program is performing?</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="large-2 cell">
                  <img class="arrow show-for-large" src="img/arrow.png">
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid-container info">
              <div class="grid-x grid-padding-x">
                <div class="large-12 cell">
        <p>In the first 90 days:</p>
<p>After performing our initial audit, we will have a baseline understanding of your SEO efforts.  You can expect us to make sure you are operating at peek efficiency when it comes to your SEO over the course of our program. 

	<p>We will provide bi-weekly reports (and check-ins if desired) with ranking information, traffic, etc. compiled from various tracking tools.  We will provide feedback on how things are going and where we think things could be.</p>
</p>
<p>We will also have a visualization tool that will allow you to see where you can improve in terms of your SEO set up.  This “at a glance” tool will be great for you and your team to see how you are performing over all.</p>
<p>Beyond 90 days:</p>
<p>Search engine optimization and content creation strategies take time, but from the day of your initial audit to day 90 to day 145, you will start to see increased organic traffic that is searching for your keywords of interest.
</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
